    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you start by managing a small courier shop and delivering food orders across the city. Players can buy new vehicles and hire employees with the money they earn by completing deliveries on time. Additionally, you have the opportunity to expand your courier business by acquiring different licenses. The demo version allows you to fully experience the core mechanics of the game, but it offers limited delivery tasks, vehicle options, and trading opportunities in terms of content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo Contents</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delivery Tasks:</strong> Ensure customer satisfaction and earn income by making timely deliveries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras/bdb9869d474eb6ed2106b37a4ab8bb38.avif?t=1729795292\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras_big/bdb9869d474eb6ed2106b37a4ab8bb38.avif?t=1729795292 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vehicle Development:</strong> Purchase new vehicles to increase your delivery capacity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras/cc5002a68ab21900783b7a3d568d7a00.avif?t=1729795292\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras_big/cc5002a68ab21900783b7a3d568d7a00.avif?t=1729795292 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Employee Management:</strong> Hire new employees to grow your company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras/286bfe10adfa0d446b76d5dbe1ee7e06.avif?t=1729795292\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras_big/286bfe10adfa0d446b76d5dbe1ee7e06.avif?t=1729795292 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Licenses:</strong> Expand your transportation business with new product licenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras/cdaf59bf9ca4f2c37b80baf9c0959dcf.avif?t=1729795292\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras_big/cdaf59bf9ca4f2c37b80baf9c0959dcf.avif?t=1729795292 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Growth:</strong> Use different strategies to establish the most profitable business model.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras/69bd760f251080ec8d6d2407f97dd3b7.avif?t=1729795292\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270830/extras_big/69bd760f251080ec8d6d2407f97dd3b7.avif?t=1729795292 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full version offers much more! Discover how far you can grow your business with car races, gambling, more employees, vehicles, licenses, and surprise features!</p></li></ul>",
